---
layout: base.njk
title: Услуги 
description: Полагане на подови замазки в Пловдив - машинно полагане, подово отопление, открити площи и много повече.
permalink: uslugi.html
---

<!-- Services Grid Section -->
<section class="section-padding ">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-globus-black mb-4">Нашите Услуги</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-globus-black/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">От машинно полагане до специализирани решения - предлагаме пълна гама от услуги за вашия проект</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for service in services %}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] shadow-lg overflow-hidden border border-globus-light-gray hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
        <!-- Service Image -->
        <div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="{{ pathPrefix }}{{ service.image }}" 
            alt="{{ service.title }}"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Service Content -->
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-globus-black mb-3 group-hover:text-globus-red transition-colors duration-300">
            {{ service.title }}
          </h3>
          <p class="text-globus-black/70 mb-4 line-clamp-3">
            {{ service.description }}
          </p>
          
          <!-- Benefits Preview -->
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-globus-black mb-2">Основни предимства:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              {% if service.benefits %}
                {% for benefit in service.benefits %}
                <li class="text-sm text-globus-black/60 flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  {{ benefit }}
                </li>
                {% endfor %}
              {% endif %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- CTA Button -->
          <a 
            href="{{ pathPrefix }}uslugi/{{ service.slug }}" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-globus-red text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-[10px] hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:shadow-lg"
          >
            Детайли
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.line-clamp-3 {
  display: -webkit-box;
  -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
  overflow: hidden;
}
</style> 